Class StartProcessingMessagePolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.camel.support.ServiceSupport
      • org.apache.camel.support.RoutePolicySupport
        • org.openhubframework.openhub.core.common.processingmessage.StartProcessingMessagePolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Service, ShutdownableService, RoutePolicy, StatefulService, SuspendableService

    public class StartProcessingMessagePolicy
extends RoutePolicySupport
    Policy that check if ESB is stopped and refused with exception StoppingException all incoming call. Input route is recognized by method RouteDefinitionService.isInputRoute(RouteTypeInfo).
    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Roman Havlicek
    See Also:
    RouteDefinitionService.isInputRoute(RouteTypeInfo), RouteTypeEnum.INPUT, RouteTypeResolver, StartProcessingMessagePolicyFactory
